OL,3,CSenior Israeli commander indicates IDF
OL,4,Cwere behind Gaza white flag shooting
OL,6,FThe IDF has given the strongest
OL,7,Findication yet that one of their
OL,8,Fsoldiers was behind the shooting of an
OL,9,Funarmed civilian in Khan Younis, ITV
OL,10,FNews Senior Correspondent John Irvine
OL,11,Freports
OL,13,FA senior commander in the Israel
OL,14,FDefence Force (IDF) has given the
OL,15,Fstrongest indication yet that Israeli
OL,16,Fforces were responsible for killing a
OL,17,Fman who was part of a group waving a
OL,18,Fwhite flag in Gaza, in footage
OL,19,Fbroadcast by ITV News.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G1/14
