OL,3,CSenior Israeli commander indicates IDF
OL,4,Cwere behind Gaza white flag shooting
OL,6,FThe IDF initially dismissed the video,
OL,7,Fwhich was broadcast on January 23,
OL,8,Fclaiming the footage "is clearly
OL,9,Fedited and we have no way to comment".
OL,11,FBut in an interview with ABC News,
OL,12,FBrig. General Dan Goldfuss, commander
OL,13,Fof the IDF 98th Division, revealed
OL,14,Fthey are now investigating the
OL,15,Fincident but remained adamant his
OL,16,Ftroops do not fire at civilians,
OL,17,Fadding: "There are mistakes, it is
OL,18,Fwar".
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/14
