OL,3,CSenior Israeli commander indicates IDF
OL,4,Cwere behind Gaza white flag shooting
OL,6,FThe person who fires the fatal shot is
OL,7,Fnot seen in the video, but before the
OL,8,Fgunfire, the camera pans around the
OL,9,Fscene which shows what appears to be
OL,10,Fan Israeli tank positioned nearby.
OL,12,FWhen questioned over the footage
OL,13,Ffilmed by a cameraman, employed by ITV
OL,14,FNews to cover the war in Gaza, General
OL,15,FGoldfuss said: "Yes, those are my
OL,16,Ftroops and I'm investigating that
OL,17,Fincident.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/14
