OL,6,F"That is not the way we carry out our
OL,7,Frules of engagement. No, we don't fire
OL,8,Fat people waving white flags. We don't
OL,9,Ffire at civilians."
OL,11,FBrig. General Dan Goldfuss, commander
OL,12,Fof the Israel Defence Forces' 98th
OL,13,FDivision, is questioned by an ABC
OL,14,Fjournalist over the footage filmed by
OL,15,Fan ITV News cameraman
OL,17,FWhen the ABC journalist responded
OL,18,F"but, you do sometimes", Goldfuss
OL,19,Freplied: "We don't."
