OL,6,FHe continued: "There are mistakes, it
OL,7,Fis war. This is not a machine working,
OL,8,Fthese are people."
OL,10,FThe footage was broadcast on January
OL,11,F23 and has sparked outrage from
OL,12,Fmembers of the UK parliament and
OL,13,Fleading charities, including Amnesty
OL,14,FInternational and the Norwegian
OL,15,FRefugee Council, who have described it
OL,16,Fas "evidence of a war crime".
