OL,6,FWhen questioned by ITV News last week,
OL,7,FPrime Minister Rishi Sunak did not
OL,8,Fcondemn the shooting as a 'war crime'
OL,9,Fbut said he is "concerned" about the
OL,10,Floss of civilian life in the enclave.
OL,12,FJan Egeland, the leader of the
OL,13,FNorwegian Refugee Council told ITV
OL,14,FNews: "It's an absolutely shocking
OL,15,Fvideo... civilians are protected,
OL,16,Fprecautions should be taken to shield
OL,17,Fthem - it's not debatable the law is
OL,18,Fvery clear.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G6/14
