OL,3,CSenior Israeli commander indicates IDF
OL,4,Cwere behind Gaza white flag shooting
OL,6,F"If it was the Israel Defence Force
OL,7,F(IDF) you could charge commanders
OL,8,Fhere, it's utterly important there
OL,9,Fwill be accountability."
OL,11,FFrancesca Albanese, UN Special
OL,12,FRapporteur on the occupied Palestinian
OL,13,Fterritories, described the incident as
OL,14,F"a televised war crime".
OL,16,FShe added: "What kind of justification
OL,17,Fcan be found for the killing of
OL,18,Fsomeone waving a white flag? From that
OL,19,Fdistance? What kind of danger were
OL,20,Fthose people posing? They were just
OL,21,Ftalking to some journalist."
