OL,6,FOne of the men - Ramzi Abu Sahloul -
OL,7,Fis interviewed and says he was
OL,8,Fattempting to reach his mother and
OL,9,Fbrother to escort them out of harm's
OL,10,Fway.
OL,12,FOnce the interview is complete, the
OL,13,Fgroup of men continue on their way -
OL,14,Fwhen the cameraman turns to get one
OL,15,Flast picture of the group, a round of
OL,16,Floud shots can be heard.
