OL,6,FThe five start to run, but Mr Abu
OL,7,FSahloul collapses on the ground. The
OL,8,Fgroup then drag his body back down the
OL,9,Froad, as blood soaks the white flag,
OL,10,Fthat has been laid across his chest.
OL,12,FLater in the video, another round of
OL,13,Fgunshots can be heard and the group of
OL,14,Fcivilians are seen hiding next to Mr
OL,15,FAbu Sahloul's lifeless body.
