OL,6,FMr Abu Safia explained to ITV News it
OL,7,Fwas the victims family who had urged
OL,8,Fhim to release the footage of that
OL,9,Fday, as he described the moment Mr Abu
OL,10,FSahloul was killed "in front of his
OL,11,Feyes".
OL,13,FMilitary vehicles circled nearby as
OL,14,Fthe cameraman interviewed the group,
OL,15,Fand Mr Abu Safia said he noticed a
OL,16,Flaser beam coming from the gun of a
OL,17,Fnearby sniper.
