OL,6,FHe said: "I heard a sniper's gun fire.
OL,7,FThat was the only fire noise. I
OL,8,Fstopped recording, and I was wondering
OL,9,Fif I was in danger or if it was a
OL,10,Fwarning firing. I realised then the
OL,11,Fman was shot."
OL,13,FMr Abu Safia stopped recording for
OL,14,Faround five seconds after hearing the
OL,15,Fgunfire, but decided he needed to
OL,16,Fdocument what was happening, so began
OL,17,Frecording again.
