OL,6,F"I approached slowly to see what
OL,7,Fhappened to the man. I saw how the man
OL,8,Fwas shot in his heart. His sons came
OL,9,Fto him to take him. They tried to
OL,10,Fcarry him, we were fired at again," he
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,F"If they wanted us to leave they
OL,14,Fshould've aimed in the air to warn us
OL,15,Fand make us leave. They didn't do
OL,16,Fthat. The man was shot before my eyes.
OL,17,FThey tried to save him but couldn't.
OL,18,FIt was a direct shot to his heart," he
OL,19,Fadded.
